## Rule 8 — Complete `AppRouteMeta` Field Reference

Every route meta field. Fields not listed here MUST NOT be invented.

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `title` | `string` | Page title (tab, breadcrumb) |
| `titleKey` | `string` | i18n key (preferred over `title`) |
| `parent` | `LayoutMode` | Layout shell: `'admin'` / `'fullscreen'` / `'ratio'` |
| `rank` | `number` | Sidebar order weight (lower = higher up) |
| `roles` | `string[]` | Role-level route guard |
| `auths` | `string[]` | Button-level permission strings |
| `keepAlive` | `boolean` | Cache component on route leave |
| `icon` | `string` | Menu icon identifier |
| `showLink` | `boolean` | Show in sidebar menu (default `true`) |
| `hidden` | `boolean` | Hide route entirely |
| `hideBreadcrumb` | `boolean` | Suppress breadcrumb for this route |
| `fixedTag` | `boolean` | Pin this tab (cannot be closed by user) |
| `hiddenTag` | `boolean` | Exclude from tabs bar entirely |
| `activeMenu` | `string` | Highlight this sidebar path when on this route |
| `isLink` | `boolean` | Route is an external URL |
| `linkUrl` | `string` | The external URL (used when `isLink = true`) |
| `reuseWindow` | `boolean` | Focus existing window instead of opening new one |
| `backstage` | `boolean` | Set by `processAsyncRoutes` — marks backend-sourced routes |
| `ratio` | `string` | Aspect ratio for `parent='ratio'` layout (e.g. `'16:9'`) |
| `parentPaths` | `string[]` | Ancestor paths (auto-injected by transform) |
| `transition` | `object` | Page-level route transition override (see below) |

**`transition` sub-fields:**

```typescript
meta.transition = {
  name?: string            // CSS transition class name
  enterTransition?: string // Enter animation class
  leaveTransition?: string // Leave animation class
  duration?: string        // e.g. '0.5s' or '500ms'
}
```
